      <title>中国人民银行抑制债券市场上涨，收益率曲线趋陡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-06/china-s-yield-curve-steepens-as-pboc-pushes-back-on-bond-rally</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国的主权债券收益率曲线正在趋陡，此举可能会受到当局的欢迎，因为干预的威胁促使交易员放缓购买长期债券的速度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-06/china-s-yield-curve-steepens-as-pboc-pushes-back-on-bond-rally</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 04:01:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
